{"tid":1808083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］當和理非遇上裝修情況指南","createTime":"2020-01-02T06:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T07:14:16.000Z","uid":160528,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27ab8d1e062745af22aa8b97b79d9aa7425fdcac","tid":1808083,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.咩都唔會做/唔同意和平示威時段裝修但唔割嘅人：</span></span><br />\n走快兩步 預多少少直位比人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.想幫忙而又唔敢落手嘅人：</span></span><br />\n手上有雨傘就立即幫人擋風擋雨<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.承上一點如果太多雨傘 唔需要你嘅時候：</span></span><br />\n請係附近觀望一下周圍有冇d似鬼嘅人 唔係叫你捉 係留意佢 當佢想上前分化/好似琴日果兩個中抗咁嘅時候 拉走佢 左膠都同樣待遇<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論 歡迎各位意見提供 預防再次發生同樣情況<br />\n<br />\n利申：依家周圍都有工程 想大家行街安全d"},{"pid":"8ffc348ab0e9c08741113d4d3369f15d81eda50a","tid":1808083,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:56:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbae750153c2061ea6319b3a8ed8ce3d3c72c2eb","tid":1808083,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"417b9ee200a9e84663931cd1162f093d6f4deb0c","tid":1808083,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:58:21.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d93467ddc5aef5fd947fbca35b5a1c3561df63a7","tid":1808083,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7dbb8f538eec33dfa7625af2b6f560a8033834e7","tid":1808083,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56dae984d7b1948e4552b1bd37b86fc7a6d2ddcb","tid":1808083,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"20ae